                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2"><locus target="#127r" facs="129"/><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1031VirginAndChild">Virgin and Child</ref>. Child is in the right arm</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3"><locus from="127v" facs="130"/><locus to="128r" facs="130"/><desc>Four <ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1041HolyMen">Holy Men Potrait</ref> (The Four Evangelists?)</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d4"><locus target="#128v" facs="131"/><desc>An ornate <ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1071Cross">Cross</ref> written in pencil</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d5">
                    Decorative designs:
                    <locus target="#1r" facs="003"/> (large ornate ḥaräg in red and black ink);
                    <locus target="#6v #13r #19v #28r #34v #39v #47r #56r #62r #66r #76r #87r #89v #95r #111r #117r #124r" facs="009 015 022 030 037 042 049 058 064 068 078 089 092 097 113 119 126"/> (ornate ḥaräg in red, black, and green ink);
